course_description: This course synthesizes the ENP role as leader, mentor, educator and/or policy developer to advocate for and ensure the delivery of safe and equitable emergency care.
prerequisites: NRSG 811D as prerequisite, NRSG 812D and NRSG 814D as co-requisites, or equivalent transfer credit.
